---
// Animated gold line that grows from 0% to 100% width on scroll
---

<div class="py-4 flex justify-center">
  <div class="gold-line-grow animate-on-scroll w-full max-w-xs h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #C8A55A, transparent);"></div>
</div>

<style>
  .gold-line-grow {
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 1s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1);
  }
  .gold-line-grow.visible {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }
</style>
